videos.headline: Werts breaks out for big gain
videos.description: Shai Werts scrambles to the outside for a 28-yard gain to put Georgia Southern in the red zone.

videos.headline: Williams finds open space for long run
videos.description: Appalachian State RB Marcus Williams takes the sweep and breaks out to the outside for a 21-yard gain in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Lamb finds Reed wide open for TD
videos.description: Appalachian State QB Taylor Lamb leads his TE Collin Reed into the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Southern makes statement with stop on fourth down
videos.description: On fourth-and-1, Appalachian State RB Marcus Williams tries rushing up the middle, but is denied by Monquavion Brinson for a huge stop.

videos.headline: Lamb puts App State in great scoring position with QB sneak
videos.description: Appalachian State QB Taylor Lamb decides to rush up the middle and finds an opening for a 44-yard gain late in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Mountaineers come out firing to start second half
videos.description: On the first offensive play of the third quarter, Appalachian State QB Taylor Lamb finds WR Thomas Hennigan down the field for a 51-yard gain.

videos.headline: Mountaineers execute fake punt
videos.description: Appalachian State DL Caleb Fuller takes the redirect snap and rushes it for 23 yards.

videos.headline: Lamb's 2nd TD extends Appalachian State's lead
videos.description: On the first play of the fourth quarter, Appalachian State QB Taylor Lamb lofts a pass to WR Ike Lewis in the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Lamb puts Mountaineers in red zone with big pass
videos.description: On fourth-and-6, Appalachian State QB Taylor Lamb completes a pass down the sidelines to WR Ike Lewis for a 30-yard gain.

videos.headline: Harrington dashes up the middle for 1st career TD
videos.description: Appalachian State RB Daetrich Harrington takes the carry up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown.
